  "an3.183-352:1.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3",
  "an3.183-352:2.1": "18. Rāgapeyyāla",
  "an3.183-352:3.1": "183–​352",
  "an3.183-352:4.1": "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā.",
  "an3.183-352:4.2": "Katame tayo?",
  "an3.183-352:4.3": "Suññato samādhi, animitto samādhi, appaṇihito samādhi—",
  "an3.183-352:4.4": "rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā. <span class=\"brnum\">(1)</span> <span class=\"var\" title=\"(rāgassa bhikkhave abhiññāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā. katame tayo? savitakkasavicāro samādhi, avitakkavicāramatto samādhi, avitakkaavicāro samādhi. rāgassa bhikkhave abhiññāya ime tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā.) etthantare pāṭho katthaci dissati, aṭṭhakathāyaṃ\" id=\"note462\">()</span>",
